concept.label: lsda:Hardware
concept.short-comment: A much shorter list than the others as you might expect since it only involves subjects!

concept.label: lsda:HardwareType
concept.short-comment:
LSDC categories can be further grouped into: - Instruments (measures something or is used to measure something) - ExperimentApparatus (needed to conduct an experiment but doesn't measure anything - e.g. bunsen burner, test tubes, pulleys, rope, sampling kits, green record logs) - Health/safety equipment - equipment used to maintain the health and safety of crew members (e.g., syringe, first aid kit, bungee cords, space suit, flight couch) but does not include instruments including medical instruments - Miscellanious hardware such as the space exploration vehicle and the crew transport vehicle
